Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multi-objective optimization, which is a common topic in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of probabilistic factorizations, which is a topic that falls under the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new class of models, which could potentially fall under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
